== 制作 ==
本片由Lilies Films公司和France 3 Cinéma联合出品<ref>{{cite web |title=Petite Maman de Céline Sciamma (2021) |url=https://en.unifrance.org/movie/52040/petite-maman |website=UniFrance |accessdate=2021-02-16 |language=en}}</ref>。这也是制片人贝内迪克蒂·库夫勒尔、摄影师克莱尔·马彤继[[燃燒的女子畫像|《燃烧女子的肖像》]]后再度与瑟琳·席安玛携手合作。影片于2020年11月在巴黎郊外开机拍摄<ref>{{cite web |author1=Keslassy, Elsa |title=Celine Sciamma Shooting New Movie "Petite Maman" in France |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/celine-sciamma-petite-maman-filming-1234825938/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2020-11-09 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313100235/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/celine-sciamma-petite-maman-filming-1234825938/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本片由Pyramide负责法国发行，MK2负责国际发行<ref>{{cite web |author1=Lemercier, Fabien |title=Appealing new titles for mk2 Films at the online AFM |url=https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/394855/ |website=Cineuropa |accessdate=2020-11-15 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309180543/https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/394855/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 首映 ==
本片入选[[第71屆柏林影展|第71届柏林国际电影节]]主竞赛单元，并于2021年3月3日在柏林国际电影节首映<ref>{{cite web |author1=Berlinale press office |title=Competition - Reshaping Cinematic Forms |url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/press/press-releases/detail_64272.html |website=Berlinale |accessdate=2021-02-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212152335/https://www.berlinale.de/en/press/press-releases/detail_64272.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Sharf, Zack |title=Berlin Film Festival Lineup 2021: New Films by Céline Sciamma and Hong Sang-soo Enter Competition |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/02/berlin-film-festival-lineup-2021-1234615521/ |accessdate=2021-02-12 |publisher=IndieWire |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227015214/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/02/berlin-film-festival-lineup-2021-1234615521/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在柏林线上首映期间，Neon公司即洽购此片北美发行权，MUBI公司洽购此片英国、爱尔兰和土耳其发行权<ref>{{cite web|author1=Welk, Brian|title=Neon Acquires Celine Sciamma's Berlinale Contender 'Petite Maman'|url=https://www.thewrap.com/neon-acquires-celine-sciamma-petite-maman-berlinale-contender/|website=The Warp|accessdate=2021-03-03|language=英语|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309222418/https://www.thewrap.com/neon-acquires-celine-sciamma-petite-maman-berlinale-contender/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Keslassy, Elsa |title=MK2 Films Sparks Bidding War With Celine Sciamma's 'Petite Maman' |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/global/celine-sciamma-petite-maman-berlinale-mk2-sales-1234931830/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2021-03-16 |language=英语 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317092340/https://variety.com/2021/film/global/celine-sciamma-petite-maman-berlinale-mk2-sales-1234931830/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年6月2日《小妈妈》在法国公映，8月27日在土耳其公映，9月15日在荷兰公映，11月19日在英国公映。

